            <title>[FELIX-3413] NPE and thread blocked in org.osgi.service.packageadmin.PackageAdmin#refreshPackages(Bundle[])</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3413</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;NPE and thread is blocked, when PackageAdmin#refreshPackages(bundleArray) is called under the following conditions:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Bundle[] bundleArray = &lt;/p&gt;
{BundleA, null, BundleB}

&lt;p&gt;call PackageAdmin#refreshPackages(bundleArray)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;StackTrace:&lt;br/&gt;
Exception in thread &quot;FelixFrameworkWiring&quot; java.lang.NullPointerException&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.felix.framework.BundleRevisionDependencies.getDependentBundles(BundleRevisionDependencies.java:163)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.felix.framework.Felix.populateDependentGraph(Felix.java:4059)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.felix.framework.Felix.refreshPackages(Felix.java:3898)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.felix.framework.FrameworkWiringImpl.run(FrameworkWiringImpl.java:172)&lt;br/&gt;
        at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:595)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
